# Machine-local secrets for zsh.
# Created once by chezmoi; later local edits are preserved.
#
# This file is NOT tracked in git. Add your API keys and tokens here.
# Format: one KEY=VALUE pair per line.
# No spaces around the '=' sign. Quotes around values are allowed (e.g., KEY="value with spaces").
# Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
#
# --- Example variables (uncomment and fill in) ---
# CONTEXT7_API_KEY=your-context7-api-key
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key
# GITHUB_TOKEN=your-github-token
# OPENCODE_LOGGING=info
